      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about the money though. it's the fact that i was supposed to be the one who made it. now i'm just this massive disappointment to everyone who believed in me. every time i think about trying to \"fix\" it or start over, i just feel this crushing weight in my chest. it feels like the only way to actually stop the shame is to just... not have to deal with it anymore. like, is there even a point in trying to rebuild when the version of me they knew is already dead?",
